  "title": "Technical Sales Engineer #76952",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Construction</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Technical Sales Engineer</strong></li><li>Working Location: Pioneer</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (Mon to Fri 8.30AM – 6PM)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary up to $4,500 + $600 (Transport Allowance) + Petrol card + Profit Sharing (Quarterly basis) + Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Provide technical knowledge and sales support to prospective and existing clients in the construction industry.</li><li>Assess client needs and recommend suitable solutions, ensuring our offerings meet their technical requirements.</li><li>Conduct technical presentations and demonstrations to highlight the benefits and features of our products and services.</li><li>Develop and maintain strong relationships with key clients, stakeholders, and industry professionals.</li><li>Prepare and present detailed proposals, including cost estimates, project timelines, and technical specifications.</li><li>Create and execute strategic sales plans to achieve and exceed sales targets.</li><li>Any other ad-hoc duties as assigned.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in Engineering, Construction or relevant discipline.</li><li>At least 2 years of sales experience in the relevant industry.</li><li>Must possess own transport vehicle.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#76952 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
